article.description: — Paul Scruggs had 24 points as Xavier got past Butler 68-55 on Saturday.
article.headline: Scruggs scores 24 to carry Xavier over Butler 68-55
article.linkText: Scruggs scores 24 to carry Xavier over Butler 68-55
article.story: INDIANAPOLIS -- — Paul Scruggs had 24 points as Xavier got past Butler 68-55 on Saturday. Adam Kunkel had 15 points for Xavier (11-2, 4-2 Big East Conference). Nate Johnson added 14 points. Zach Freemantle had 10 rebounds. Bryce Nze had 16 points and 11 rebounds for the Bulldogs (5-9, 4-7). Bo Hodges added 11 points and six rebounds. Aaron Thompson had 10 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
